						<p class="publication_time">December 12, 2010</p>
				
						<h2>Storm Clouds, Utah</h2>

						
							<p class="credit">Photograph by <a href="http://ngm.nationalgeographic.com/myshot/gallery/99991#/gallery/947022/">Steven Besserman</a>, My Shot</p>
												

						<p><b>This Month in Photo of the Day: <a href="http://travel.nationalgeographic.com/travel/travel-photos/?source=pod">Travel</a> and <a href="http://adventure.nationalgeographic.com/photography?source=pod">Adventure</a> Photos</b></p>

<p> Storm clouds move in over a Utah cornfield at sunset. </p>

<p><em>(This photograph was submitted to <a href="http://ngm.nationalgeographic.com/myshot/">My Shot</a>.)</em></p>

